dc_title_s: Ciudad de Quito : plano de nomenclatura - sectorización y distritos
dc_description_s: Relief shown by 10 meters contours. Oriented with North toward top right corner. Map shows districts located by color coded, construction areas, urban limits, roads, railways, important buildings, colleges, churches, and oil pipeline. Map includes index for city districts. Includes indexes of street names ; public buildings ; parks, plazas, and gardens. "Publicado por el I.G.M. en base a la ordenanza municipal no. 1496 del 21 de julio de 1972. Quito abril--1983."
